did.head: Overview
did.unittitle: Stanford University, Department of Physics, honors theses
did.abstract: Honors theses written by undergraduates in the Stanford University Department of Physics.

repository.label: Repository:
repository.corpname: Department of Special Collections and University Archives

acqinfo.p: Theses were transferred to the Stanford University Archives by the Department of Physics in 1997, by the Physics Library in 2010-2011, and by the Hume Writing Center in 2011.

accessrestrict.head: Information about Access
accessrestrict.p: This collection is open for research; materials must be requested at least 48 hours in advance of intended use. No photocopies may be made.

userestrict.head: Ownership & Copyright
userestrict.p: Copyright is retained by the creators for materials they have authored or otherwise produced. Transmission or reproduction of materials requires the written permission of the copyright owner.

prefercite.head: Cite As
prefercite.p: [Identification of item], Stanford University, Department of Physics, Honors Theses (SC4-4471). Dept. of Special Collections and University Archives, Stanford University Libraries, Stanford, Calif.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: This collection consists of honors theses written by undergraduates in the Stanford University Department of Physics.
